<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Denise Van Outen dressed up to the nines to leave her cabaret show at Proud Embankment on Monday night. </p>

<p>The former Big Breakfast icon, 46, looked incredible wearing a black and white zebra print mini dress as she was pictured leaving Proud Embankment. </p>

<p>She wore a pair of heeled ankle boots as she headed out to her waiting car and added a pop of colour to her look with a slick of bright red lipstick.</p>

<p>Striking! Denise Van Outen wore a zebra print mini dress to leave her cabaret show at Proud Embankment in London on Monday as she's tipped for the next series of Dancing On Ice</p>

<p>Denise has been starring in a Vegas style show, with a line up of live music and cabaret stars.</p>

